thread.title: Anne-Marie O'Neill
thread.title_full: Initial Hygiene IE reviewed by Anne-Marie O'Neill

author: Anne-Marie O'Neill
title: Anne-Marie O'Neill
text: Chris always comes and changes our mats regularly and does an excellent job. It keeps our school looking very clean and tidy and is a very good way of ensuring as little dirt comes in from the outside as possible. Initial hygiene are very professional and provide a very efficient service.
